#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.68"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.68:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Devatāvagga"
msgstr "7. A God"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Saṅgaṇikārāmasutta"
msgstr "68. Enjoying Company"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.423"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.68:1.1"
msgid ""
"“‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṅgaṇikārāmo saṅgaṇikarato saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ "
"anuyutto, gaṇārāmo gaṇarato gaṇārāmataṃ anuyutto, eko paviveke abhiramissatī’"
"ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, it’s totally impossible that a mendicant who enjoys company and "
"groups, who loves them and likes to enjoy them, should take pleasure in "
"being alone in seclusion."

msgctxt "an6.68:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘Eko paviveke anabhiramanto cittassa nimittaṃ gahessatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ "
"vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without taking pleasure in being alone in seclusion, it’s impossible to "
"learn the characteristics of the mind."

msgctxt "an6.68:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘Cittassa nimittaṃ agaṇhanto sammādiṭṭhiṃ paripūressatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ "
"vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without learning the characteristics of the mind, it’s impossible to fulfill "
"right view."

msgctxt "an6.68:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘Sammādiṭṭhiṃ aparipūretvā sammāsamādhiṃ paripūressatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ "
"vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without fulfilling right view, it’s impossible to fulfill right immersion."

msgctxt "an6.68:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘Sammāsamādhiṃ aparipūretvā saṃyojanāni pajahissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without fulfilling right immersion, it’s impossible to give up the fetters."

msgctxt "an6.68:1.6"
msgid "‘Saṃyojanāni appahāya nibbānaṃ sacchikarissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without giving up the fetters, it’s impossible to realize extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.68:2.1"
msgid ""
"‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na saṅgaṇikārāmo na saṅgaṇikarato na "
"saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ anuyutto, na gaṇārāmo na gaṇarato na gaṇārāmataṃ anuyutto, "
"eko paviveke abhiramissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"It’s totally possible that a mendicant who doesn’t enjoy company and groups, "
"who doesn’t love them and like to enjoy them, should take pleasure in being "
"alone in seclusion."

msgctxt "an6.68:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘Eko paviveke abhiramanto cittassa nimittaṃ gahessatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"For someone who takes pleasure in being alone in seclusion, it’s possible to "
"learn the characteristics of the mind."

msgctxt "an6.68:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘Cittassa nimittaṃ gaṇhanto sammādiṭṭhiṃ paripūressatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"For someone who learns the characteristics of the mind, it’s possible to "
"fulfill right view."

msgctxt "an6.68:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘Sammādiṭṭhiṃ paripūretvā sammāsamādhiṃ paripūressatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "Having fulfilled right view, it’s possible to fulfill right immersion."

msgctxt "an6.68:2.5"
msgid ""
"‘Sammāsamādhiṃ paripūretvā saṃyojanāni pajahissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "Having fulfilled right immersion, it’s possible to give up the fetters."

msgctxt "an6.68:2.6"
msgid "‘Saṃyojanāni pahāya nibbānaṃ sacchikarissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti."
msgstr "Having given up the fetters, it’s possible to realize extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.68:2.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
